realize that it kept <em>speaking</em> to me, day after day, and week after week.
It wanted to grow. It wanted to be nurtured.</p>

<p>So finally, I decided,</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>I am going to allow that thread to be nurtured. And I‚Äôm going to
discover where it takes me, and what it‚Äôs all about.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>And where it took me was into mastery of life and death, mastery of
healing, mastery of consciousness. It took me into mastery of myself. It
brought me home to my own Christed Beingness.</p>

<p>Because I followed that thread, I can talk with you today. There are
many of you that appreciate what I have done, because you see me as a
spokesperson for the Truth. Is it not time that <em>you</em> followed your <em>own</em>
thread, and became, likewise, a spokesperson for reality? For just as
you have been sent to <em>me</em>, there will be many sent to <em>you</em>, as you step
from being a <em>seeker</em> to a <em>finder</em>. For as you take up your right place,
you become a vehicle through which the Voice for God will creatively
