<p>And then you will know the Truth that sets you free:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Of myself, I do nothing. But my Father, through me, does all things. And
it is very good.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Be you, therefore, at peace. And <em>desire well</em>. For when you feel desire,
